{"tid":665534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最激一次！欣宜床戰鄧健泓：張被畀人扯開","createTime":"2018-05-15T04:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T05:22:27.000Z","uid":88167,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"182b69f433cc9339c93dea5c82c802f513412807","tid":665534,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"藝人何佩瑜（Jeana）、鄭欣宜、雨僑及連詩雅等下午云集中環，為網劇《性敢中環》開工。Jeana與欣宜孖住受訪，談到劇中難忘場面，欣宜笑謂：「我獻出咗螢幕最激嘅一次床戲。（同邊個？）人夫鄧健泓，我都好期待同佢合作，覺得佢好生鬼，大家產生到化學作用。（好性感？）冇諗過露嘅都露咗，張被畀人扯開。」她又笑言自己是「動作演員」：「可能我中文唔好，所以文戲唔得，反而『動作戲』1 take起2 take止！」<br />\n<br />\nJeana封胸晒腳<br />\n<br />\n至於Jeana則「封胸」現身，問到是否簽約英皇後改路線，她笑謂：「今日都有腳睇，夏天呀，有雀斑。（有冇親熱戲？）同栢天男咀，事前佢有啲緊張，所以同佢傾吓偈，輕鬆吓先。」此時欣宜聞言笑說：「當年拍MV我都同佢咀過，不過最終個shot冇出到！（食唔少『好嘢』喎，最想再同邊個拍先？）金城武，呢個型男橫跨過幾個年代，係堅嘅男神！」<br />\n<br />\n為左大家著想所以無貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180514%2Fbkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html&d=8sqKBRi0yiYERUZG5XD7RNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=21a52cb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ef09d6c2620e4e375972d398b6da88a6843f1de","tid":665534,"uid":63588,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/124906_8704857329061a1a1b0bbe8054cfd8f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F124906_8704857329061a1a1b0bbe8054cfd8f7.png&h=dafd45bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5493ac0f1483bd20b83a721d9ba54db8eeba3f29","tid":665534,"uid":140767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"冇諗過露嘅都露咗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d3dda1a79b47794f78b4e396601579fcb79fb0","tid":665534,"uid":140767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"不如我地..."},{"pid":"8cf3524c22c35fe1ef85a4c811172abe726fb4a5","tid":665534,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e601f8de8f11a3e840f6fb6491c52eb7889250a","tid":665534,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"最癡線係Jeana 冇床戲但欣宜有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9971f6d1d39c882ee96b8c83d2441efe94fa24f","tid":665534,"uid":88167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e601f8de8f11a3e840f6fb6491c52eb7889250a","tid":665534,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"最癡線係Jeana 冇床戲但欣宜有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"製造話題既野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beb24c9c15a37a1e6bf78d718ca4e38b29d80fa","tid":665534,"uid":3480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"欣宜床戰鄧健泓: 鄧健泓畀我扯開"},{"pid":"670acdd3de5856d5cdce3841fc648af4c2c0382e","tid":665534,"uid":140390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"Jeana一定係淫底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次係台灣西門町間阿性情趣用品店見佢拎住枝假9笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c294e118e18657d01a1b4a41e50a11e4998aa472","tid":665534,"uid":163750,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藝人何佩瑜（Jeana）、鄭欣宜、雨僑及連詩雅等下午云集中環，為網劇《性敢中環》開工。Jeana與欣宜孖住受訪，談到劇中難忘場面，欣宜笑謂：「我獻出咗螢幕最激嘅一次床戲。（同邊個？）人夫鄧健泓，我都好期待同佢合作，覺得佢好生鬼，大家產生到化學作用。（好性感？）冇諗過露嘅都露咗，張被畀人扯開。」她又笑言自己是「動作演員」：「可能我中文唔好，所以文戲唔得，<span style=\"color: red;\">反而『動作戲』1 take起2 take止！</span>」<br />\n<br />\nJeana封胸晒腳<br />\n<br />\n至於Jeana則「封胸」現身，問到是否簽約英皇後改路線，她笑謂：「今日都有腳睇，夏天呀，有雀斑。（有冇親熱戲？）同栢天男咀，事前佢有啲緊張，所以同佢傾吓偈，輕鬆吓先。」此時欣宜聞言笑說：「當年拍MV我都同佢咀過，不過最終個shot冇出到！（食唔少『好嘢』喎，最想再同邊個拍先？）金城武，呢個型男橫跨過幾個年代，係堅嘅男神！」<br />\n<br />\n為左大家著想所以無貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180514%2Fbkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html&d=8sqKBRi0yiYERUZG5XD7RNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=21a52cb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n[black]有無諗過係導演唔想繼續NG先局住收貨[/black]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ec9a3487651300cdd77a39bf583780c5417ba0","tid":665534,"uid":165336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂鄧健泓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c66ddf98669f5051a5cc0c0f1301dc4588e7c1a","tid":665534,"uid":51436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"鄧健泓：我絕對冇強姦隻豬"},{"pid":"83926ba1fabffd6ff6f9c242a3a00e5b4784ab8d","tid":665534,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182b69f433cc9339c93dea5c82c802f513412807","tid":665534,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"藝人何佩瑜（Jeana）、鄭欣宜、雨僑及連詩雅等下午云集中環，為網劇《性敢中環》開工。Jeana與欣宜孖住受訪，談到劇中難忘場面，欣宜笑謂：「我獻出咗螢幕最激嘅一次床戲。（同邊個？）人夫鄧健泓，我都好期待同佢合作，覺得佢好生鬼，大家產生到化學作用。（好性感？）冇諗過露嘅都露咗，張被畀人扯開。」她又笑言自己是「動作演員」：「可能我中文唔好，所以文戲唔得，反而『動作戲』1 take起2 take止！」<br />\n<br />\nJeana封胸晒腳<br />\n<br />\n至於Jeana則「封胸」現身，問到是否簽約英皇後改路線，她笑謂：「今日都有腳睇，夏天呀，有雀斑。（有冇親熱戲？）同栢天男咀，事前佢有啲緊張，所以同佢傾吓偈，輕鬆吓先。」此時欣宜聞言笑說：「當年拍MV我都同佢咀過，不過最終個shot冇出到！（食唔少『好嘢』喎，最想再同邊個拍先？）金城武，呢個型男橫跨過幾個年代，係堅嘅男神！」<br />\n<br />\n為左大家著想所以無貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180514%2Fbkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html&d=8sqKBRi0yiYERUZG5XD7RNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=21a52cb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180514/bkn-20180514151543143-0514_00862_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢其實可以直頭唔貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb342d9de9770e6b89e2b2d378313681dcaf9a2b","tid":665534,"uid":22913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"吳卓羲比欣宜咀咗一啖就霉到宜家"}]}